data.description: IMPROVED PRICE! Wonderful modern living in a popular neighborhood. Prime location near schools and shopping. Enjoy newer paint throughout the home, providing a clean and contemporary aesthetic. Enjoy cooking in an open kitchen equipped with newer stainless steel appliances. Two living spaces, a formal living area, and a family living room provide versatility and room to spread out. The front yard boast no-maintenance artificial grass, rock, and decorative rock on the exterior. Must see!
